title: Getting Started with Microsoft Office SharePoint Server 2016
sessionTitle: Getting Started with Microsoft Office SharePoint Server 2016
eventShortDescription:
​In this session, we will explore the design goals and features of Office SharePoint Server 2016. You also manage documents and Web content using Office SharePoint Server 2016. We will cover:

  • The design goals and features of Office SharePoint Server 2016
  • How to manage documents and Web content using Office SharePoint Server 2016
  • The Office SharePoint Server 2013 features for organizing and finding data
  • How to implement business solutions using Office SharePoint Server 2016
